Dia. 01 Double Sente
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par After Black 1 and 3, White ends up with gote with 4. So it is a sente endgame for Black.
\par
\par If White would play the hane, it would be sente for White as well, so it is a double sente. These double sente moves \cf1\b should be played first \cf0\b0 in the endgame.
\par
\par
\par }
