Dia. 02 Borderline
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par As always the borderlines are made by Xs.
\par Black has 14 points and White has 10 points.
\par
\par At first it is good to count the territory one by one point. Later if you become expert in counting it is possible to count like two, four, six, etc...
\par
\par }
