Dia. 03 Also Sente for White
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par As it was said before, even if White plays it is also sente.
\par Moreover, against White 1 Black can't block directly.
\par
\par After Black pulls back with 2, White can go one more at 3.
\par This time it is \cf1\b White's sente endgame\cf0\b0  up to 6.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
