Dia. 04 Double Sente, 6 Points
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is the same shape like in the previous diagram and the borderlines are made with Xs.
\par
\par Black has 10 points, White has 12 points.
\par
\par After counting it is
\par (14-10)+(12-10)=\cf1\b 6 points\cf0\b0 .
\par Therefore, this endgame on the first line is \cf2\b double sente\cf0\b0  and worth\cf2\b  6 points\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
