Dia. 05 Gote
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White can play the side attachment at 1.
\par It is a \cf1\b 7 points gote endgame\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par \cf2\b Which is better, sente 6 points or gote 7 points?
\par \cf0\b0
\par The answer is obvious. It is strange to end up in gote just for one extra point.
\par
\par However, if there is no other endgame left, the best sequence is from White 1 to 7.
\par
\par
\par }
